data.description: Gorgeous 2 Story Home with Full Basement! 1.28 Acre Horse Property In Widely Desired Todd Creek Riverside Community. 3 Bedrooms, 3 Baths , including an Open Den Upstairs with Full Upgrades. Gorgeous Views Of The Front Range. Store Your RV, Camper, Or Toys Inside The 1360 Sq Ft Outbuilding With 220 AMP Power And Concrete Floor. Could Also Be Used For A Shop, Or Barn! Also Includes A 132 Sq Ft Shed and  Chicken Coop. Enjoy A Spacious Backyard With Plenty Of Areas To Enjoy Our Beautiful Colorado Atmosphere and Sunsets! Livestock Welcomed on Property (Chickens, Goats & Horses). Granite Counters And Oak Cabinetry Complete With Stainless Steel Appliances And Large Pantry. Handcrafted Stamped Concrete Patio. Full Basement WITH Added Room For Storage.  Dimensions for shop are: 34 x 40 sq ft Shop. 16' height  Doors are 12' x 14' and 9' x 9' plus Home has an attached 3 car garage. Enjoy Country Living While Being Minutes from Downtown Brighton. Close to Restaurants, Shopping and Entertainment. Extremely Close To Both I-25 and Highway 85, Giving You Easy Access South To Denver Or North To Fort Collins/Loveland/Greeley!
